<template>
   <el-table
            :data="page"
            border
            style="width: 100%">
        <el-table-column
            prop="applyRecordId"
            label="申请序号">
        </el-table-column>
        <el-table-column
            prop="name"
            label="用户名"
        >
        </el-table-column>
        <el-table-column
            prop="account"
            label="工号">
        </el-table-column>
        
        <el-table-column
            prop="duringTime"
            label="请假天数">
        </el-table-column>
        <el-table-column
            prop="state"
            label="请假状态"
            >
        </el-table-column>
        <el-table-column
            prop="type"
            label="请假类型">
        </el-table-column>
    </el-table>
  </template>

  <script>
  export default ({
      data(){
          page:[]
      },
      methods:{
          loadTable() {
            var empId = window.sessionStorage.getItem('empId');
            this.$http.get('/getApplyRecordById/'+empId).then(res => {
                console.log('res');
                console.log(res);
                // _this.page = res.data;
                // console.log(_this.page);
            });
        },
      }
  })
  </script>
